# DEFPROCwindow_poll
Msg01:~1;31mOther side lost carrier...
Msg02:~33mChat finished...
Msg03:~32mPress [?] or [Return] if nothing happens...


# DEFPROCio()
Msg04:This door allows you to send a message (and optionally chat) to any user
Msg05:currently on-line. To abort, press Ctrl+C. Ctrl+\ for information.
Msg06:~44m~37m  # ~36mBaudR ~37mUser# ~36mUsername                       ~37mWhere       ~40m


# DEFPROCshowstats... Special case DOING strings.
Msg07:Logging on
Msg08:New user


# DEFPROCgetport
Msg09:~32mWhich port would you like to send your message to? ~33m

Msg10:~37mHmmm... What's a negative port? An 'antiport' - the BBS calls you? ;-)
Msg11:~37mHmmm... How many ports do you think there are??? ;-)
Msg12:~37mWhoops!!!
Msg13:~37mTalking to yourself again? You should seek help if this continues...
Msg14:~37mSorry, that port is not on-line at this time.
Msg15:~37mSorry, that port has not completed log-on procedure yet.


# DEFPROCgetmessage
Msg16:~32mPlease enter your message, up to two lines, and press RETURN to send.~33m
Msg17:~36mWould you like the option of a private chat (Y/n) ?


# DEFPROCsendtoport
Msg18:~35mSorry,"+esc$+"37m the port you are trying to contact has disconnected...
Msg19:~37m the port you are trying to contact has disconnected...
Msg20:~35mSorry,~37m the port you are trying to contact is running another door...

Msg21:~37mAttempting to send...

Msg22:~33mSorry, the user doesn't want to be bothered by chat requests or messages...

Msg23:~32mMessage from %0 on port %1...
Msg24:~36m%0

Msg25:~33mSent!

Msg26:35mSorry,~37m port %0 is unobtainable. Please check and try again.


# DEFPROCgetuser - used if invalid username found.
