Msg32:Message from Parlez door

Msg33:~33mYour message has been uploaded to %0's mailbox...


# DEFPROCinitiatechat()
Msg34:~36mAsking if other user would like to open a private chat...
Msg35:~36mWould you like to open a private chat with %0 (Y/n)? 
Msg36:~35mTimed out...
Msg37:~35mUser didn't want to chat...
Msg38:~35mChat cancelled...

Msg39:~33mChat started...  Press ^C to finish or ^T for remaining time.


# Colours used in chat:
#   Us typing, on our screen     - 36 (Cyan)      | So echoed text is cyan,
#   Us typing, on their screen   - 37 (White)     | and text from the other
#   Them typing, on our screen   - 37 (White)     | side is white...
#   Them typing, on their screen - 36 (Cyan)
Msg40:~36m
Msg41:~37m
Msg42:~37m
Msg43:~36m

Msg44:~1;31mOther side lost carrier...


# DEFPROCcloseup
